---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About HostHive" description="Learn about HostHive's mission, testing methodology, and editorial standards.">
  <article class="legal-page">
    <span class="page-label">About</span>
    <h1>Independent hosting reviews<br/><em>you can trust.</em></h1>

    <section>
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>HostHive helps you make informed decisions about web hosting. We provide independent reviews based on real performance data -- uptime monitoring, speed benchmarks, and hands-on testing.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>How We Test</h2>
      <p>Every hosting provider we review goes through comprehensive testing:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Uptime monitoring</strong> over 30+ days with minute-by-minute checks</li>
        <li><strong>Speed benchmarks</strong> using GTmetrix, Pingdom, and custom load testing</li>
        <li><strong>Support evaluation</strong> via live chat, tickets, and phone across multiple time zones</li>
        <li><strong>Migration testing</strong> to assess ease of moving sites between providers</li>
        <li><strong>Scaling tests</strong> to see how hosting handles traffic spikes</li>
        <li><strong>Value analysis</strong> comparing features per dollar across plans</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Editorial Independence</h2>
      <p>Affiliate commissions never influence our reviews. We recommend hosting we'd use ourselves. Every review includes both strengths and weaknesses.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions or hosting you'd like us to review? Email <a href="mailto:info@host-hive.net">info@host-hive.net</a>.</p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page { max-width: var(--max-width); margin: 0 auto; padding: var(--space-3xl) 0; }
  .page-label { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--ink-400); display: block; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
  .legal-page h1 { margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl); }
  .legal-page h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--ink-500); }
  .legal-page section { margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl); }
  .legal-page h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-md); margin-top: 0; }
  .legal-page p { color: var(--ink-700); line-height: 1.8; }
  .legal-page ul { padding-left: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); }
  .legal-page li { color: var(--ink-700); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
  .legal-page strong { color: var(--ink-950); }
  .legal-page a { color: var(--violet); }
  .legal-page a:hover { color: var(--violet-hover); }
</style>
